p.k: Egg Hunt / Bucket List / TV Knight 6 / Kryptonite Robin still regrets not being able to find an Easter egg when he was a kid, so the Titans head to Gotham to solve this mystery. / The Titans give Starfire a bucket list of activities to accomplish. / Batman is forced to go to the department store with Alfred, but runs off to watch TV with Commissioner Gordon. / When Robin explains that knowing your weakness makes you a better superhero, Starfire journeys to find hers.
